Paper: hep-th/0103010

Date: 2001-03-01

Title: Quantum Energies of Interfaces

Authors: N. Graham, R. L. Jaffe, M. Quandt, and H. Weigel

Comments: 8 pages, 1 figure, minor changes, Phys. Rev. Lett., in print

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 87 (2001) 131601

We present a method for computing the one-loop, renormalized quantum energiesof symmetrical interfaces of arbitrary dimension and codimension usingelementary scattering data. Internal consistency requires finite-energy sumrules relating phase shifts to bound state energies.